&gt;&gt;Male #1: I love older people.

00:34:52.669 --> 00:34:55.520
I respect older people.

00:34:55.520 --> 00:34:59.080
I live for older people.

00:34:59.080 --> 00:35:04.060
'cause I come from somebody that's older.

00:35:04.060 --> 00:35:11.890
So first and foremost, I wanna say, we did
do wrong.

00:35:11.890 --> 00:35:16.880
We did things, we stuck on ourself.

00:35:16.880 --> 00:35:20.300
We did a lot of wrong things.

00:35:20.300 --> 00:35:21.300
You know.

00:35:21.300 --> 00:35:29.050
And for the most part, it's I don't respect
how you look down on us.

00:35:29.050 --> 00:35:30.300
You treat us a certain type of way.

00:35:30.300 --> 00:35:31.300
It's alright.

00:35:31.300 --> 00:35:32.300
We gonna do it for the next 30 years.

00:35:32.300 --> 00:35:33.300
We gonna show you all.

00:35:33.300 --> 00:35:34.300
We gonna do what we gotta do.

00:35:34.300 --> 00:35:35.300
But my whole thing is, my first and foremost.

00:35:35.300 --> 00:35:36.300
