00:41:40.050 --> 00:41:41.050
community.

00:41:41.050 --> 00:41:42.130
F--- that shit.

00:41:42.130 --> 00:41:43.130
I'm black.

00:41:43.130 --> 00:41:44.570
I'm proud of that.

00:41:44.570 --> 00:41:48.790
And I don't have to adhere to all these cultural
norms in order to prove that.

00:41:48.790 --> 00:41:53.970
&gt;&gt;Male #7: See, I've always believed in dealing
