00:58:02.400 --> 00:58:10.930
But as the people doing the selection curation
of this material, and deciding how to present

00:58:10.930 --> 00:58:16.849
it and which parts of it to present to the
people who interact with it or, and become

00:58:16.849 --> 00:58:21.990
a part of the project, in that way or to the
