00:59:04.599 --> 00:59:06.960
And which ones are the ones that you might
try to suppress?

00:59:06.960 --> 00:59:13.349
&gt;&gt; Chris Johnson: Well, I think the essence
of that goes back to the fact that as I said

00:59:13.349 --> 00:59:19.770
