01:00:33.130 --> 01:00:37.430
And then you use formal strategies, of course
the framing.

01:00:37.430 --> 01:00:40.690
And I talked a little bit about the way the
installation is designed.

01:00:40.690 --> 01:00:42.599
You know try to be inclusive.

01:00:42.599 --> 01:00:47.250
Those are all things that are driven by our
sensibilities as artists.

01:00:47.250 --> 01:00:52.220
And then we hope that experience is transformative
for the viewers.

01:00:52.220 --> 01:00:57.100
&gt;&gt;Hank: Well, I agree with him to a degree.

01:00:57.100 --> 01:01:03.400
