idea of an authoritative narrative voice.

01:01:59.980 --> 01:02:04.400
That within especially social sciences says,
I have an expert from the outside that's gonna

01:02:04.400 --> 01:02:11.950
come in and apply these generic kind of format
to finding out information about a certain

01:02:11.950 --> 01:02:12.950
group.

01:02:12.950 --> 01:02:14.589
Whereas our project is really organic.

01:02:14.589 --> 01:02:17.530
you know, Chris will walk up to somebody on
the street.

01:02:17.530 --> 01:02:19.400
Or Bayete will call somebody in another place.

01:02:19.400 --> 01:02:21.990
Or Kamal will say, oh I happen to know.

01:02:21.990 --> 01:02:24.380
Everybody happens to know some black man somewhere.

01:02:24.380 --> 01:02:28.050
So the diversity is implied in the way that
we find people.

01:02:28.050 --> 01:02:34.170
